    "description_long": "This is a sleek, low-profile sports car with a streamlined body and aggressive front fascia, featuring a wide grille and angular headlights. The car has a coupe design with two doors, tinted windows, and a smooth, aerodynamic roofline that tapers towards the rear. The wheels are large, black, and have a multi-spoke design, contributing to its sporty appearance. The rear of the car includes distinctive taillights, dual exhausts, and a subtle integrated bumper. The exterior is finished in a matte gray color, with black accents on the wheels and window trims. The overall design suggests high performance and luxury, suitable for urban streets or upscale neighborhoods.",
